import React from 'react'
import { Col, Container, Row } from 'react-bootstrap'
const Blog = ({ blog }) => (
  <Container>
    <Row>
      <Col>
        <label>{blog.title}</label>
        <label>{blog.author}</label>
        <label>{blog.url}</label>
        <label>{blog.likes}</label>
        <label>{blog.user.name}</label>
      </Col>
    </Row>
 </Container>
)

export default Blog
